PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,FHussein's reign was defined by fierce
OL,8,Foppression and murderous attacks on
OL,9,Fhis opponents, notoriously gassing
OL,10,Fthousands of Kurds to death in the
OL,11,Flate 1980s, while rumours abounded
OL,12,Fthat dissenting voices in his cabinet
OL,13,Fwould be taken out and shot.
OL,15,FWithin months of the ITN interview,
OL,16,FIraqi forces would go on to massacre
OL,17,Fhundreds of thousands of Shia and
OL,18,FMarsh Arabs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,FAcknowledging his interviewee's
OL,8,Fruthless reputation, Sir Trevor
OL,9,Frevealed the filming in Iraq was also
OL,10,Fnot without jeopardy for him and his
OL,11,Fcolleagues.
OL,13,F"You know, we were walking into the
OL,14,Funknown," he told Bradby. "And I'm not
OL,15,Fusually a person who sort of enjoys
OL,16,Fthat.
OL,18,F"The first thing is an element of
OL,19,Fterror. It's the unpredictability of
OL,20,Fit. There's no format, there's no
OL,21,Fformula."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,FHe said the ITN team was kept in limbo
OL,8,Ffor more than a week before eventually
OL,9,Fbeing "roughed up" and strip-searched
OL,10,Fen route to the interview.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,F"There was even a point where they
OL,18,Fsaid, 'I'm not too sure you can take
OL,19,Fyour cameras with you,'" Sir Trevor
OL,20,Frecalled. "I said, 'What? But we're
OL,21,Fgoing to do a television interview...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,F"Unpredictability was the game. And we
OL,8,Fnever knew from one moment to another
OL,9,Fwhat was going to happen."
OL,11,FBy contrast, Sir Trevor recounted the
OL,12,Fquietly comical scenes that had played
OL,13,Fout weeks earlier in Iraq's Cultural
OL,14,FOffice in London's Tottenham Court
OL,15,FRoad as the then-newsreader doggedly
OL,16,Fpursued the landmark Hussein interview
OL,17,Fby cultivating a relationship with an
OL,18,FIraqi official.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,FSir Trevor recounted how the crucial
OL,8,Fslip of paper with a formal reply to
OL,9,Fhis interview request got lost under a
OL,10,Fmountain of paperwork in the
OL,11,Fofficial's haphazard office, before he
OL,12,Ffinally received an unexpected home
OL,13,Fphone call weeks later with the
OL,14,Fdefining message: "Baghdad will see
OL,15,Fyou now."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,FWhile Hussein cut a composed figure on
OL,8,Fcamera, Sir Trevor recalled the leader
OL,9,Fwas left rattled in the half hour that
OL,10,Ffollowed filming, pacing the Baghdad
OL,11,Fpalace floor while seeking to further
OL,12,Fjustify his attack on the neighbouring
OL,13,FKuwait amid international outcry.
OL,15,F"I think he was not unaware of what
OL,16,FIraq's position was," Sir Trevor said.
OL,17,F"And in the end, it was going to end
OL,18,Fas it was going to end."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,FWhile Iraq swiftly lost the Gulf War
OL,8,Fin 1991 in the face of the Western-led
OL,9,FOperation Desert Storm, Hussein's
OL,10,Fbrutal reign continued until the US-
OL,11,Fdriven invasion in 2003. He was
OL,12,Fsentenced to death by an Iraqi court
OL,13,Fin 2006 for crimes against humanity.
OL,15,FReflecting on the state of Iraq today,
OL,16,FSir Trevor said: "There is still a
OL,17,Ffeeling of sadness about what may have
OL,18,Fbeen several years later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,F"Saddam represented one side of the
OL,8,Freligious divide. He supported the
OL,9,FSunnis. And there was an understanding
OL,10,Fin some parts of the world, I remember
OL,11,Ftalking in Kuwait, in fact, to an
OL,12,FIrish contingent of people who were
OL,13,Fthere who (were) drawing on the
OL,14,Fexperience of what happened in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland as a way of trying to
OL,16,Fbring the different forces together,
OL,17,Fthe different peoples together. And
OL,18,Fnothing like that happened.
OL,20,F"The divisions are now more profound
OL,21,Falmost than ever.
OL,26,@uD@KpmuD@Ppn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,F"I wonder whether a chance (has been)
OL,8,Fmissed about trying to change that
OL,9,Foutcome? Difficult, perhaps
OL,10,Fimpossible. But I just wonder whether
OL,11,Fenough of a chance was made about
OL,12,Fchanging that?"
OL,14,FYou can view Sir Trevor McDonald's
OL,15,Freflections on his seminal interview
OL,16,Fwith Saddam Hussein in Reporting
OL,17,FHistory on ITVX and YouTube. The
OL,18,Fextended audio conversation with Tom
OL,19,FBradby is also available on any
OL,20,Fpodcast platform.
OL,26,@oD@\pmoD@epn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
