OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,FThe limited series also includes
OL,8,Fremarkable testimony from ITV News
OL,9,Fcorrespondents who have found
OL,10,Fthemselves in astonishing situations
OL,11,Fwhile capturing the news.
OL,13,FAmong the episodes is International
OL,14,FEditor Emma Murphy's remarkable
OL,15,Faccount of coming face-to-face with an
OL,16,Farmed and dangerous Raoul Moat in the
OL,17,Fsummer of 2010 while reporting on his
OL,18,Fmurderous shooting spree that sparked
OL,19,Fone of Britain's largest manhunts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
