OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772752279
OL,3,CSir Trevor McDonald reveals question
OL,4,Che asked Saddam Hussein makes him
OL,5,C'cringe'
OL,7,FAnd Correspondent John Ray describes
OL,8,Fin thrilling detail how he and an ITN
OL,9,Fteam were held hostage by Colonel
OL,10,FGaddafi's forces before escaping in
OL,11,Fthe dying days of the Libyan
OL,12,Fdictator's regime in 2011.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
